node.text:
I have been using @purekana CBD products for over 2 years, and really love everything about them.
.
It’s served a variety of different PHYSICAL purposes in my active life. From helping me achieve deep and valuable REM sleep at night, to easing my joint and muscle pain from rigorous training methods.
.
The PHYSICAL benefits only scratch the surface for me, as the MENTAL gains from this pure form of CBD are the real heightened area of improvement!
.
I was someone who was diagnosed late in life with Tourette’s syndrome, and battled a lot of mis-diagnosis, leading to experimenting with medications my whole life. I was basically a lab rat for counselors, and up until my thirties had never found true balance or peace in life during times of high anxiety or stress. I would shut down, and find myself trying to climb out of an imaginary hole I wasn’t even in...
.
Fast forward to finding @purekana — those issues of overwhelming anxiety and stress have ceased nearly completely. My ticks, and muscle spasms although still present have diminished to almost not being noticeable.
.
This is not a drug. This isn’t a pill. This isn’t a prescription or harmful, and defendant chemical you’re putting into your body..
.
This is a natural, plant derived, premium form of hemp that can help you function at a higher and more efficient frequency, without any sort of psychoactive ‘High’ or side effect to list.
.
Although CBD may not be everyone’s first choice of natural relief, it will forever be mine, and I reach for #Purekana when I do.
.
#PlantsNotPills #natural #Ad #Sponsored #Pk #TeamPk #educational #informative #Learning #Pure #legal #alexTurner

node.text:
DAY 2- NO THC 👌🏽
.
I’ve been going to bed earlier the last couple of nights, getting extremely restful nights of sleep with little to no interruptions. I’ve been waking up excited. I am ready to tackle the planet, and anything that wants to stand in my way! This is new for me… and I hate to admit it. But for a very long time. I woke up and faked my happiness. I tried to find the drive to push through the day, and most of the time did it high as hell or smoking weed constantly throughout it.—I was depressed. Unhappy. And finding crutches and people to help make me feel complete.
.
Rewind to yesterday: I woke up for the first time in a very long time, STOKED to be alive. Grateful to have the day in front of me. Ready to take on anything and everything…and it allll hit me. I had been holding myself back in so many ways mentally and emotionally by masking my depression or anxiety vs working at fixing it and finding the root of it all. Needless to say, I didn’t let it defeat me having this realization, I instead, allowed myself the ability to forgive my own choices, and to move on in a different way going forward.
.
For me, I am no longer putting substances into my body to numb, take away emotion, or lift my mind in false ways that I need not do. I am focusing solely on my nutrition, supplementation, exercise, and of course my sleep. Between these areas and parts of the equation, I see that without substance abuse present, will change my life in ways I’ve never gotten to experience. 
.
So here’s to the fact I ❤️ cannabis, but also see it’s not as beneficial for MY own life as much as it may be for some of you! And that’s okay! You shouldn’t feel wrong in using it if it makes you happy or helps, snd I know for a lot of people it does! For my highly functioning brain, this just isn’t conducive anymore to my happiness or success and I’m ready to try new things and experience life through new eyes!
.
So as much as I know there will be people who judge this and criticize it, I’m CHOOSING to embrace all of you who support me with this. Thank you all. Let’s cheers our @fitaid ‘s like the Baddies we are, and SEIZE THIS DAY!! ⚡️
.
#inked #tattoos #tattoo #new #healthy

node.text:
⚡️PLEASE READ⚡️
.
TIME AND PLACE FOR STIMS
.
.
I have promoted using pre-workout for over a decade, and for every individual there is always something that feels or works better then it may for the next person.
.
I’ve paid a lot of attention to trends, and popular preferences over the years and a lot of these “hyped up” products, contain insane amounts of stimulants.
.
Here’s my thing…👌🏽
.
The human body can only process so much caffeine in a day before you begin having/experiencing side effects that directly take away from your overall physical health!
.
Stimulants can cause restless nights of sleep, even when ingested earlier in the day. It can cause irregular sleep patterns, resulting in sleep quality non conducive for recovery or muscle rebuilding. Remember, our sleep is literally 1/3 of this entire equation, and when you start playing with your sleep, you’re playing with fire.
.
Secondly, high amounts of stimulant can cause blood vessels to constrict which can result in LACK of blood flow, therefore lack of pump!
.
We WANT to get maximum vasodilation & blood vessel expansion so we can get adequate blood into those muscles for a fulfilling and beneficial workout!
.
Aside from having a much more focused, and blood-filled workout, you will hold your pump longer, and get a great night sleep following your workout, no matter the time of day!
.
I am a HUGE promoter of non-stimulant preworkouts for a multitude of reasons, those above being a few!
.
THIS is why I LOVE the Pumptropic by @gatsupplements as my choice, stim-free preworkout at the moment 🤘🏽⚡️😎🔥
.
(Flavor preference is strawberry mango 🤤)
.
.
Click the link in my bio to check these all-new products out, and as always message me with ANY questions regarding what is best for your goals!! 😎🔑
.
.
📸 @sab_shotit
.
.
